         | firstname | lastname | number | context | cti_profile | cti_login | cti_passwd |
         | Gonzales  | DaCosta  | 1044   | default | Client      | gonzales  | dacosta    |
        When I start the XiVO Client
        When I set auto-reconnect interval to "5" seconds
